No information.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF326A8DFF87923B1FF8BFCB" pageId="201" pageNumber="963" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF326A8DFF87923B1FF8BFCB" blockId="201.[121,1329,293,1435]" pageId="201" pageNumber="963">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF326A8DFF87923B1FDDBFB0" bold="true" box="[123,477,1121,1155]" pageId="201" pageNumber="963">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. The Malaysian Whiskered 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF326A8DFE7692D31FE4BF99" authority="Kaup, 1829" box="[394,484,1162,1195]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="201" pageNumber="963" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Myotis</taxonomicName>
is known only from a few specimens, and little is known about its distribution, abundance, ecology, or conservation threats. It occurs in Belum-Temenggor Forest Reserve.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
